OL,3,CBlock of unstable flats in Plymouth
OL,4,Cdeemed safe
OL,6,FPeople living in and around a block of
OL,7,Funstable flats in Plymouth have been
OL,8,Ftold they'll be able to return home
OL,9,Fthis morning (Wednesday, 27 May).
OL,11,FEvolution Cove in Durnford Street,
OL,12,FStonehouse, was evacuated in March,
OL,13,Fafter structural engineers found it
OL,14,Fwas at risk of collapse. Props have
OL,15,Fnow been installed in the underground
OL,16,Fcar park to stabilise it.
OL,18,FBoth Plymouth City Council and Devon
OL,19,Fand Somerset Fire and Rescue Service
OL,20,Fhave confirmed that the building is
OL,21,Fsafe enough for residents to return.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
