OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780143067
OL,3,CBlock of unstable flats in Plymouth
OL,4,Cdeemed safe
OL,6,FAuthorities have been working
OL,7,Fovernight to remove fencing, cones,
OL,8,Fcables and signs set up as part of an
OL,9,Fexclusion zone. More than a dozen
OL,10,Fhouseholds near the flats, which were
OL,11,Falso evacuated, can also return home
OL,12,Ftoday.
OL,14,FTraffic should also return to normal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
