PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780143067
OL,3,CBlock of unstable flats in Plymouth
OL,4,Cdeemed safe
OL,6,FIn a statement on Tuesday, 26 May,
OL,7,FPlymouth City Council said: "A meeting
OL,8,Ftook place today between the building
OL,9,Fowners, engineers, and Council
OL,10,Fstructural experts, as well as the
OL,11,Ffire and rescue service, to discuss
OL,12,Fthe remediation work.
OL,14,F"The work involved installing props
OL,15,Fwithin the underground car park and
OL,16,Fthis was followed by a short period of
OL,17,Fmonitoring to check its stability.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
