PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780143067
OL,3,CBlock of unstable flats in Plymouth
OL,4,Cdeemed safe
OL,6,F"The Council's independent structural
OL,7,Fexperts then reviewed a report
OL,8,Fprovided by Clancy, the structural
OL,9,Fengineers to verify the findings.
OL,11,F"As a result, the Council's Section 77
OL,12,FOrder and Fire Service's Prohibition
OL,13,FNotice have been lifted ` meaning
OL,14,FEvolution Cove residents can return
OL,15,Fhome."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
