PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780143067
OL,3,CBlock of unstable flats in Plymouth
OL,4,Cdeemed safe
OL,6,FGlenn Caplin-Grey, Strategic Director
OL,7,Ffor Growth added: "We know this has
OL,8,Fnot been an easy time for anyone ` the
OL,9,Fresidents of Evolution Cove, their
OL,10,Fneighbours who had to leave their
OL,11,Fhomes and the residents and businesses
OL,12,Fof the wider Stonehouse peninsula.
OL,14,F"We would just like to say thank you
OL,15,Ffor bearing with us."
